# Component Syntax — Phase 4

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Components are implemented in Phase 4.
> This fixture is a placeholder for future tests.

The planned syntax:

```zolto
@component Card title="" variant="default"
  ### {title}
  [slot default][/slot]
@/component

<Card title="Hello">
  Content inside the card.
</Card>
```
